    <questiontext format="html">
      <text><![CDATA[<p class="HELM_exercise">Exercise<br></p>
<p>Given that \(\underline{a} = {@a_vec@}\) and \(\underline{b} = {@b_vec@}\) find \(\underline{a}+\underline{b}.\)</p>
<p>\(\underline{a}+\underline{b}=\) [[input:ans1]] [[validation:ans1]] \(\underline{i}\) \(+\) [[input:ans2]] [[validation:ans2]] \(\underline{j}\)</p>
<p>[[feedback:r]]</p>]]></text>
    </questiontext>
